page.title: 15Fore names given to children
page.content: This page is a record of the{first {names}given to children in this village during the late 1970's and early 1980's. {The most popular boys names}are James(6),John(5),Peter(4),Paul(3),Andr ew(3),Philip(3),David(3),Mark(2),Willi am(2) {The most popular girls names}are Elizabeth(5),Mary(3),Louise(2),Helen(2 ),Catherine(2),.The names that occur once are Adrian, Fraser,Graeme, Ian, Edward, Gareth, Ross, Martin, Chistopher, Terry, Richard, Henry, Amory, Robbie, Darren, Daniel, Joseph, Shaun and Timothy.The girls names that occur once only are Julie, Claire, Caroline, Abigail, Kirsty, Wendy, Tracey, Marie, Rachael, Michaela Emily, Laura and Emma. {Figures in brackets show frequency of {occurence.}
